title: For Sale/Trade:   Rare FEG AMD-65
postcontent: This is a rare like new TGI FEG AMD-65 with about 400 rounds down the pipe. It is a rock solid shooter. Lightweight, accurate and the built in compensator takes out almost all of the recoil of the 7.62x39mm cartridge. It is unique, solidly built and my personal favorite AK variant. It is completely of Hungarian Military manufacture, the only exception being a Tapco G2 trigger for 922(r) compliance. This rifle was imported in limited numbers in 1999-2000 then converted by TGI in 2004 after the AWB expired. They are rare, no longer imported and you will not find any other fully Hungarian manufactured AMD-65s on the US market. Nor will you find any of higher quality.
